# ReGenesis 🌍

ReGenesis is an AI-powered smart sustainability and emergency response system designed to monitor environmental conditions, detect hazards, and provide real-time alerts using sensors, automation, and intelligent analysis.

## Features

- Gas Leak Detection
- Temperature Monitoring
- Smart Alert System
- AI-Based Automation
- Real-Time Monitoring
- Environmental Safety

## Tech Stack

- Arduino
- Python
- IoT Sensors
- Automation Logic

## Components Used

- Arduino UNO/Nano
- MQ2 Gas Sensor
- DHT11 Sensor
- HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor
- Buzzer
- LEDs

## Future Goals

- Mobile App Integration
- Cloud Monitoring
- AI Prediction System
- Smart Emergency Response

